.DT
remove_item_by_index
Disk World creator help
remove_item_by_index

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
remove_item_by_index -  This method removes an item by the returned index number from the add_item method.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int remove_item_by_index(int index)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^index%^RESET%^ - the index number to remove
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/basic/item.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method removes an item by the returned index number from the
add_item method.
.EP

.SH Example 1
.SI 5
int _item_number;

void bing {
   _item_numer = add_item("frog", "It wombles!");
} /* bing() */

void remove_bing() {
   remove_item(_item_number);
} /* remove_bing() */

.EI

